column1: Source: USDA Branded Food Products Database Release July 2018 Software v.3.9.5 2018-08-15
Nutrient data for: CADBURY DOUBLE DECKER CHOCOLATE BAR 80 GR, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 05034660518471
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

Ingredients: Sugar, glucose syrup, glucose-fructose syrup, vegetable fats (palm, sunflower, shea, rapeseed), WHEAT flour (with added calcium, iron, niacin and thiamin), cocoa butter, cocoa mass, dried whole MILK, dried skimmed MILK, dried whey (from MILK), fat-reduced cocoa, MILK fat, emulsifiers (E442, E471, SOYA lecithin, sunflower lecithin), dried EGG white, anti-caking agent (calcium carbonate), salt, BARLEY malt syrup, raising agent (ammonium bicarbonate), flavourings. MILK CHOCOLATE: MILK SOLIDS 14% MINIMUM. CONTAINS VEGETABLE FATS IN ADDITION TO COCOA BUTTER. MAY CONTAIN PEANUTS, NUTS. Date available: 03/27/2018 Date last updated by company: 03/27/2018
